Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这在文体上非常不愉快\N{\rENG}How stylistically displeasing. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}新一点的有更美观的抛光处理\N{\rENG}The newer ones have a nicer finish. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在制造更多的书呆子日志吗?\N{\rENG}You making more nerd notes? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么是...书呆子?\N{\rENG}What is...Nerd? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能造个句吗?\N{\rENG}Can you use it in a sentence? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.88,0:03:48.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}书呆子-\N{\rENG}Nerd--
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.19,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是个 书呆子\N{\rENG}you are a nerd. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.26,0:03:54.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶 别说了\N{\rENG}Amethyst, cut that out. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.64,0:03:56.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}正如你所见 这颗星球非常烦人 \N{\rENG}As you can see, this planet is annoying, 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.95,0:03:58.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}每个事物都如此\N{\rENG}and everything is annoying. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.97,0:04:02.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在这个星球所有的罪行中包含紫晶需要\N{\rENG}Amongst its transgressions is the need for the Amethyst
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}向永融体寻求许可\N{\rENG}to ask permission from the permafusion. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}永融体? 那是你对石榴的称呼吗?\N{\rENG}Permafusion? Is that what you call Garnet? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可以称呼她很多名字\N{\rENG}I could call her lots of things. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.15,0:04:12.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可以称呼她"两个东西"-"两个草包"!\N{\rENG}I could call her two things--two clods! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}四处游荡 好似她是一个草包一样\N{\rENG}Walking around like she's one clod. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这有什么不对吗?\N{\rENG}What's wrong with that? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她又没在战斗!\N{\rENG}She's not even fighting! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她在-你懂的-她只是在-你懂的 像个...\N{\rENG}She's--you know, she's just, you know, like a...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.02,0:04:25.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你懂的!\N{\rENG}You know! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你真算个宝石人啊 "橄榄"\N{\rENG}You're a real gem, "Perry."
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是的 我是个 宝石人\N{\rENG}Yes. I am. A gem. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 好吧 来说说史蒂文吧\N{\rENG}Okay, okay. Do Steven next. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文有什么古怪的吗?\N{\rENG}What's weird about Steven? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.37,0:04:41.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我该从何说起呢?\N{\rENG}Where do I even begin? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他算某种混血弃儿\N{\rENG}He's some sort of hybrid abomination. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我甚至都无法理解他是如何维持生命的\N{\rENG}I don't even understand how he functions. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他有机的那部分消耗了太多能量\N{\rENG}His organic half consumes so much energy
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让他不得不频繁进食 \N{\rENG}that he has to constantly feed, 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}并且他得花大把时间排泄 \N{\rENG}and he spends so much time expelling
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.40,0:04:55.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}以致有单独的房间做这件事\N{\rENG}that he has a whole room dedicated to it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 不 别的东西啊-\N{\rENG}Uh, no, something else--
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.73,0:04:58.99,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}说点别的东西啊!\N{\rENG}talk about something else! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.08,0:05:07.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}最奇怪的是 紫晶 \N{\rENG}The strangest thing is, Amethyst, 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你以为你得听她们的\N{\rENG}you think you have to listen to them. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你才是那个应该指挥的人\N{\rENG}You're the one who should be in charge! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.77,0:05:14.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈!\N{\rENG}Ha! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是你目前最好的段子了!\N{\rENG}That's your best joke yet. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.68,0:05:17.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 真的\N{\rENG}No, really. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠是个珍珠\N{\rENG}Pearl is a Pearl. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴是个融合体\N{\rENG}Garnet is a fusion. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我都猜不到他存在的目的\N{\rENG}I don't even know what he's supposed to be. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.77,0:05:24.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿!\N{\rENG}Hey! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.80,0:05:28.29,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是水晶战士中唯一一个真正的宝石人\N{\rENG}You're the only Crystal Gem that's actually a gem. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.26,0:05:31.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么?\N{\rENG}What? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你比队里其他的人的等级都要高\N{\rENG}You outrank everyone on your team. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们该听你的才对\N{\rENG}They should be listening to you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.11,0:05:38.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是个强壮的 独立的 完全正常的战士 \N{\rENG}You're a strong, singular, fully functional soldier, 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}即使实际上你是有缺陷的\N{\rENG}despite the fact that you're defective. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.00,0:05:42.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}缺陷?\N{\rENG}Defective? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊 当然 你太挫了\N{\rENG}Well, sure. You're small. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以?\N{\rENG}So? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}其实 你不该是这样的\N{\rENG}Well, you're not supposed to be. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.68,0:05:50.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等下 等等\N{\rENG}Hold on. Wait, wait. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.64,0:05:52.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我猜猜 这-\N{\rENG}Let me guess. This--
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是你出生的洞\N{\rENG}this is the hole you came out of. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}太小 太低\N{\rENG}Too small, too low, 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.57,0:05:59.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}出口的痕迹看起来相比其他洞\N{\rENG}the exit marks look about 500 years newer
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}晚了500年左右 嗯\N{\rENG}than every other hole. Hmm. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.97,0:06:03.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你出来的时候这里一定已经空了吧\N{\rENG}This place must've been empty when you came out. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.40,0:06:07.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}难怪你不知道你该长成什么样子!\N{\rENG}No wonder you have no idea what you're supposed to look like! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石\N{\rENG}Peridot. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.24,0:06:11.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我应该是什么样子?\N{\rENG}What was I supposed to look like? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}首先 你是个石英\N{\rENG}Well, you're a Quartz. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石英是魁梧 忠诚的士兵\N{\rENG}They're huge, loyal soldiers. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.88,0:06:20.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你应该再大上一倍 肩膀宽阔 令人生畏 \N{\rENG}You should be twice your size, broad-shouldered, intimidating, 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.01,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你只是在地里待了太长时间了\N{\rENG}but you simply stayed in the ground too long. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.35,0:06:24.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是说我是个错误吗?\N{\rENG}Are you saying I'm wrong? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"宝石学"上讲 没错\N{\rENG}"Gemetically"speaking, yes. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.13,0:06:31.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当你考虑这件事时 这真变得有趣啊\N{\rENG}When you think about it, it's all so funny. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶\N{\rENG}Amethyst. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.80,0:06:35.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 士兵 \N{\rENG}Hey, soldier, 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许你可以帮我拆下这块钻头\N{\rENG}maybe you can help me get this hunk of drill off. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.22,0:06:43.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}瞧 看看!\N{\rENG}See? Look at that! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能完成正常的石英能做的所有事情\N{\rENG}You can do everything a normal Quartz can do. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.06,0:06:49.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我们回去用这个糊珍珠一脸吧\N{\rENG}Let's head back and shove this thing in Pearl's face. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶 你还好吗?\N{\rENG}Amethyst, are you okay? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.88,0:06:53.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要担心\N{\rENG}Don't worry about it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦! 这真是太有爱了\N{\rENG}Oh! It's lovely. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.26,0:06:57.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}考虑到我们将使用\N{\rENG}To think we'd be using
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.08,0:07:00.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一开始引起这一切的技术来解决这一切-\N{\rENG}the same technology that started all this to fix it--
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.53,0:07:03.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这个钻头真是纯嘲讽啊!\N{\rENG}this drill is pure irony! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}实际上 它大部分是碳\N{\rENG}Actually, it's mostly carbonite. 
Dialogue: 500,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.20,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn隶书\fs48\c&H6C6F75&\bord0\shad0\pos(142,982)}钉子
Dialogue: 500,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.20,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn隶书\fs48\c&H6C6F75&\bord0\shad0\pos(224,920)}螺丝
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这会让它变得"碳讽"吗?( irony: 铁的 讽刺性的; carbon: 碳)\N{\rENG}Would that make it "carbony"? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.77,0:07:10.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 哦 哦! 紫晶!\N{\rENG}Oh, oh, oh! Amethyst! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.95,0:07:16.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看这个-嗯-节奏性粉碎器!\N{\rENG}Check out this--hmm--"rhythmatic"pulverizer. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那真是太好笑了! 我太幽默了!\N{\rENG}That's funny. I'm so funny. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.57,0:07:23.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你高兴就好\N{\rENG}Whatever, dude. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那不是正确的反应啊\N{\rENG}That was the incorrect response. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 我做这些的时候紫晶没笑诶\N{\rENG}Hey, Amethyst isn't laughing when I do these things. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么她不笑出来?\N{\rENG}Why isn't she laughing? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.72,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石 你真的伤害了她的情感了\N{\rENG}Peridot, you really hurt her feelings. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.37,0:07:36.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么?\N{\rENG}What? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在幼儿园时对她有点太过刻薄了\N{\rENG}You were pretty mean to her at the kindergarten. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.71,0:07:41.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}刻薄? 不可能\N{\rENG}Mean? No way. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.95,0:07:45.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那只是...酷 紫晶喜欢的\N{\rENG}I was being...Cool. Amethyst loved it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.42,0:07:47.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她可能只是在告诉珍珠她现在有多快乐\N{\rENG}She's probably telling the Pearl how much fun she had now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.24,0:07:50.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶 嗨 嗨! 嗨. 紫晶!\N{\rENG}Amethyst, hi, hi! Hi, Amethyst! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她-她都不愿意看我\N{\rENG}She--she won't even look at me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.88,0:07:57.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这让我感觉很...渺小\N{\rENG}It's making me feel...Smaller. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.22,0:08:00.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你感觉难受 那也是你让她感受到的\N{\rENG}You feel bad. That's how you made her feel. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.22,0:08:04.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谁在乎她感觉怎么样?\N{\rENG}Who cares about how she feels? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谁在乎你们中的任何一个?\N{\rENG}Who cares about any of you?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们都只是石头而已 \N{\rENG}You're all just rocks, 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拜倒在我的重力连接器下的红润的肮脏的土块\N{\rENG}ruddy muddy clumps beneath my gravity connectors! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.11,0:08:14.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她又一次莫名其妙的发飙了\N{\rENG}Another one of her temper tantrums. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.53,0:08:16.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很惊讶你们俩能从幼儿园正常的回来\N{\rENG}I'm surprised you two made it back from the kindergarten
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而没把对方逼疯\N{\rENG}without driving each other crazy. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这个小东西-\N{\rENG}This little thing--
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.17,0:08:24.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊啊!\N{\rENG}Aah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}上面的进展怎么样了?\N{\rENG}How's everything going up there? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很好 没什么出差错的\N{\rENG}I'm fine. There's nothing wrong. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所有事都非常顺利\N{\rENG}Everything's fine. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊! 不不不不! 停下!\N{\rENG}Aah! No, no, no, no! Stop! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.80,0:08:36.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石?\N{\rENG}Peridot? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.42,0:08:41.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}面板!\N{\rENG}The panel. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔! 等等!\N{\rENG}Whoa! Wait! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没事! 我能控制住住住!\N{\rENG}It's okay! I got I-I-I-t! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}搞毛...啊!\N{\rENG}What the...Aah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.02,0:08:53.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶!\N{\rENG}Amethyst! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.84,0:08:58.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!\N{\rENG}Aah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没什么 一切都好\N{\rENG}It's okay. Everything's okay. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这只是个钻头( drill: 钻头 演习)\N{\rENG}It was just a drill. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...橄榄石?\N{\rENG}Uh...Peridot? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊! 这只是个意外! 我发誓!\N{\rENG}Aah! It was an accident. I swear! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 别担心\N{\rENG}Hey, don't worry about it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.35,0:09:25.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们知道你不是故意启动钻头的\N{\rENG}We know you didn't mean to start the drill. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.22,0:09:28.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 是的 那也只是个意外\N{\rENG}Uh, yeah. And that was an accident, too. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.53,0:09:32.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们才走了一秒钟 \N{\rENG}We leave for one second, 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就出了乱子!\N{\rENG}and everything goes off the rails! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.66,0:09:37.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我怪奶牛\N{\rENG}I blame the cows. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 没什么 一切都好\N{\rENG}No, it's fine. It's fine. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.41,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们会将它重新制造的更强大 更好\N{\rENG}We'll rebuild it stronger, better. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们会加上安全带的 !\N{\rENG}We'll add seatbelts! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!\N{\rENG}Ah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.88,0:09:50.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 你们还好吗? 那真是惊险啊\N{\rENG}Hey, are you all right? That was a close one. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还好橄榄石救了你\N{\rENG}It's a good thing Peridot was there to save you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然 这是件好事\N{\rENG}Yes, it is a good thing. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听着 我 呃...\N{\rENG}Listen. I, um...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}说出来啊\N{\rENG}Just spit it out. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!\N{\rENG}Ugh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\ 为什么你们地球人就这么难交流?! NWhy are you earthlings so difficult?!\N{\rENG}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.88,0:10:10.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}记录日期-7-1-1-2\N{\rENG}Log date 7-1-1-2. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.35,0:10:13.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}整个星球完全颠倒了\N{\rENG}This entire planet is backwards. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.77,0:10:16.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}目前还没有任何一个正常的行为\N{\rENG}There hasn't been one instance of correct behavior
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.15,0:10:19.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}体现在水晶战士的身上\N{\rENG}exhibited by any one of these crystal gems. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我得出结论-她们全部都是有缺陷的\N{\rENG}I have concluded that they are all defective. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我也没好到哪去\N{\rENG}But I am no better. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的任务失败了 \N{\rENG}I failed my mission, 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而现在我又与敌人共事 \N{\rENG}and now I'm working with the enemy, 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.15,0:10:29.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但连这个我都做不好\N{\rENG}and I can't even get that right. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.53,0:10:33.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我显然已经"伤害"了紫晶的"感情"\N{\rENG}I have apparently "hurt"Amethyst's "feelings", 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.89,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而这不是我的本意\N{\rENG}which was not my intent. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.37,0:10:37.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果我损害了我和这里最出色的宝石人的关系\N{\rENG}If I've damaged my standing with the best gem here, 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那我犯了一个严重的错误\N{\rENG}then I've made a serious mistake. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我仍然在学习\N{\rENG}I'm still learning. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我希望你们能理解\N{\rENG}I hope you understand. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我希望自己能学会\N{\rENG}I want to understand. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很抱歉\N{\rENG}I'm sorry. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.13,0:10:51.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石 切面五 结束记录\N{\rENG}Peridot, facet five. End log. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.77,0:10:53.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}正如你所见-\N{\rENG}As you can see--
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 橄榄石!\N{\rENG}oh, Peridot! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 呃 橄榄石\N{\rENG}Hey, uh, Peridot. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢\N{\rENG}Thanks. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你仍然是个书呆子\N{\rENG}But you're still a nerd. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.15,0:11:06.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我会确保将那个添加进我的笔记的\N{\rENG}I'll be sure to add that to my notes. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.71,0:11:08.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你感觉怎么样?\N{\rENG}How do you feel? 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:10.62,0:11:11.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}高大\N{\rENG}Big. 

